  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>This is a casual action horror game that can be played in about 1 hour.<br>Includes a jump scare.<br>Please play in a darkened room.<br>Not too difficult, but requires a little imagination.<br>Please note that you cannot exit the game in the middle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2>.You rent a room in a rural town in Japan and start new life with your girlfriend.<br>However, you are plagued by small strange phenomena in the room.<br>Doing some housework and, reveal the secrets about this place.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Long and Quiet Life</h2>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857700/Mansion.png?t=1715079941\" /></span><br>A room in a small 3-story apartment in a residential area.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857700/extras/be33fe78991d9fd083ce8aa1c7e07014.avif?t=1715079941\" width=570 height=320 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857700/extras/6719983feb1119295939fb8550942019.avif?t=1715079941\" width=570 height=320 /></span><br>This room is well-lit and has a Japanese-style room.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic life</h2>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857700/extras/5c308727335d6fea6c02efc9af72a178.avif?t=1715079941\" width=570 height=320 /></span><br>Even in a new apartment, it is important to keep your room clean.<br><br>Don't forget to make yourself comfortable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857700/extras/4a88a0e4fa8d08f7d34147148e429aff.avif?t=1715079941\" width=570 height=320 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming</h2>.You are welcome to streaming.<br>Please help us promote it.",
